  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Bar Association condemns the attack",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Bar Association has issued a statement saying that it strongly condemns the forceful and violent attack by the authorities on the protestors at the Galle mouth around the Presidential Secretariat this morning (22).",
        "According to the statement issued by the Bar Association, it appeared that hundreds of military personnel and policemen were blocking the roads leading to the mouth of Galle and preventing the public from entering the area.",
        "The Law Society of Sri Lanka states in its announcement that at least two lawyers who tried to intervene at their professional level were assaulted by military personnel.",
        "According to the announcement, the videos also show unarmed civilians being attacked by the security forces."
      ],
